description: We evaluated the utility of a trimodal stationary phase (Trinity P1) in offline peptide fractionation, and found it performed similarly to ion exchange or high pH reversed phase based techniques. It is orthogonal to low pH reversed phase and uses MS compatible mobile phase solvents.
